@NODE "M04" "Requirements"

 @{fg shine}@{u}REQUIREMENTS@{uu}@{fg text}
 
 TMS itself (the CLI program) does not require anything more than
 an AMiGA. But to use it internally within YAM, you will require
 REXXMast installed (Who hasn`t got REXXMast running these days?),
 a `.signarure' file and a Taglines file.
 Oh and it would be nice if you had YAM, ehehehe :)

@ENDNODE

